  "logNo": "110154157507",
  "title": "[강남맛집] 오랜만의 회식. 강남 씨푸드레스토랑 마끼노차야",
  "addDate": "2012. 12. 14.",
  "categoryNo": "43",
  "parentCategoryNo": "1",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110154157507",
  "html_size": 189302,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110154157507\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110154157507\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">지난번 회식땐 엄청 더운날이었는데..어느새 눈이 펑펑오는 겨울이 되었네요~<img src=\"https://blogimgs.pstatic.net/smarteditor/20120724/emoticon/1_02.gif\" onload=\"setTimeout('utility.resizeImageWithId(\\'smarteditor\\/20120724\\/emoticon\\/1_02.gif\\')',200)\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" id=\"smarteditor/20120724/emoticon/1_02.gif\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5B30DC3')\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">그동안 원장님이 논문쓰랴 책 집필하랴 많이 바쁘셔서&nbsp;&nbsp;오랜만에 이수한의원 식구들이 모였습니다.</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">매번 느끼지만 회식장소 정하기 참 어렵네요^^</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">어디갈까 어디가면좋을까 고민하다가 에잇.모르겠다! </p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">전부터 가고싶었던&nbsp;씨푸드레스토랑 마끼노차야 가보자고 했습니다.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20121214_262/isuhani_1355452652547VsTC3_JPEG/20121212_171833.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"541\" height=\"404\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 541px; rheight: 404px\" id=\"20121214_262/isuhani_1355452652547VsTC3_JPEG/20121212_171833.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5B30DC3')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20121214_262/isuhani_1355452652547VsTC3_JPEG/20121212_171833.jpg?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">가보고 싶었던 곳이라 두근두근 거리며 도착!</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">기념으로 사진촬영^^</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">먼저 혼자 막 들어가시는 원장님 뒷모습.</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">그러고는 \"사진찍니? 포스팅할거지?\"</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">\"응? 저 혼자 기념으로 간직하려고 찍을거에요~\" 했으나 맛있는거 먹고 왔다고 자랑하려고 </p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">지금 이렇게 포스팅을 하고 있습니다.ㅎㅎ</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20121214_103/isuhani_1355453388282WW7O7_JPEG/20121212_175106.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"525\" height=\"391\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 525px; rheight: 391px\" id=\"20121214_103/isuhani_1355453388282WW7O7_JPEG/20121212_175106.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5B30DC3')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20121214_103/isuhani_1355453388282WW7O7_JPEG/20121212_175106.jpg?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">저흰 Dinner1부로 예약을했는데 도착하니 이미 많은분들이 식사를하고 계셨어요.</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">저희도 테이블 배정받고 식사 시작!</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20121214_140/isuhani_1355454955649UOqDC_JPEG/IMG_0031.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"527\" height=\"394\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 527px; rheight: 394px\" id=\"20121214_140/isuhani_1355454955649UOqDC_JPEG/IMG_0031.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5B30DC3')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20121214_140/isuhani_1355454955649UOqDC_JPEG/IMG_0031.jpg?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20121214_122/isuhani_13554550416506az1a_JPEG/IMG_0029.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"434\" height=\"578\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 434px; rheight: 578px\" id=\"20121214_122/isuhani_13554550416506az1a_JPEG/IMG_0029.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5B30DC3')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20121214_122/isuhani_13554550416506az1a_JPEG/IMG_0029.jpg?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">늙어보이지 않게 찍어달라고 주문하신 울 원장님.</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">원장님 미안요<img src=\"https://blogimgs.pstatic.net/smarteditor/20120724/emoticon/1_09.gif\" onload=\"setTimeout('utility.resizeImageWithId(\\'smarteditor\\/20120724\\/emoticon\\/1_09.gif\\')',200)\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" id=\"smarteditor/20120724/emoticon/1_09.gif\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5B30DC3')\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">저에겐 그런 능력이 없어요ㅜ</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">그래도 원장님 멋있어염<img src=\"https://blogimgs.pstatic.net/smarteditor/20120724/emoticon/3_32.gif\" onload=\"setTimeout('utility.resizeImageWithId(\\'smarteditor\\/20120724\\/emoticon\\/3_32.gif\\')',200)\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" id=\"smarteditor/20120724/emoticon/3_32.gif\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5B30DC3')\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20121214_121/isuhani_1355455167426KIOyz_JPEG/IMG_0030.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"427\" height=\"568\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 427px; rheight: 568px\" id=\"20121214_121/isuhani_1355455167426KIOyz_JPEG/IMG_0030.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5B30DC3')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20121214_121/isuhani_1355455167426KIOyz_JPEG/IMG_0030.jpg?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">원장님이 고르신&nbsp;와인 \"1825 카베르네 쇼비뇽\" </p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">저는 술을 잘 못해서 어떤 와인이 맛있는지 잘 모르지만.</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">원장님이 고르셨으니 맛있는 와인이겠죠^^</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20121214_189/isuhani_1355461520268BHzb7_JPEG/20121212_175129.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"521\" height=\"390\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 521px; rheight: 390px\" id=\"20121214_189/isuhani_1355461520268BHzb7_JPEG/20121212_175129.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5B30DC3')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20121214_189/isuhani_1355461520268BHzb7_JPEG/20121212_175129.jpg?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">처음부터 초밥을 먹으면 배가 불러 못먹을까봐 아껴뒀더니..</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">나중에는 못먹겠더라구요..</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">간장게장이 그렇게 맛있다던데..구경만하고 먹어보진 못했어요.</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">회원카드 만들고 왔으니 다음기회에 다시 가봐야겠어요.</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">+</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;안티구아스 레세르바스 까베르네 쇼비뇽을 주문하면 1825 까베르네 쇼비뇽 1병을 선물로 주는 이벤트가 진행중입니다.</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">여러명이 가실 계획이라면 연말에 와인으로 분위기 내보는것도 괜찮지 않을까요?</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><video src=\"https://mblogvideo-phinf.pstatic.net/20121214_87/isuhani_1355461755107IdHF6_GIF/con1_img01_4.gif?type=mp4w800\" width=\"538\" height=\"881\" id=\"20121214_87/isuhani_1355461755107IdHF6_GIF/con1_img01_4.gif\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5B30DC3')\" alt=\"\" loop=\"loop\" muted=\"muted\" playsinline=\"playsinline\" data-gif-url=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20121214_87/isuhani_1355461755107IdHF6_GIF/con1_img01_4.gif?type=w3\" class=\"_photoImage _gifmp4\">&nbsp;</video></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">마끼노차야 운영시간 및 금액입니다.</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">예약하실 때 참고하세요^^</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><video src=\"https://mblogvideo-phinf.pstatic.net/20121214_145/isuhani_1355461901787VELW0_GIF/map_img1.gif?type=mp4w800\" width=\"550\" height=\"237\" id=\"20121214_145/isuhani_1355461901787VELW0_GIF/map_img1.gif\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5B30DC3')\" alt=\"\" loop=\"loop\" muted=\"muted\" playsinline=\"playsinline\" data-gif-url=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20121214_145/isuhani_1355461901787VELW0_GIF/map_img1.gif?type=w3\" class=\"_photoImage _gifmp4\">&nbsp;</video></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
